Description:
A rare find indeed
Being offered to the general public for the first time since 1975, we find this 599.3 square metre block of land in the heart of Hoppers Crossing, frontage 16.66 metres and depth of 35.96 metres.
With no restrictive covenants the possibilities for redevelopment are many, while also offering a home site that would satisfy most home designs of today.
Situated within minutes of Pacific Werribee Shopping Centre, Mossfiel Primary School, Hoppers Crossing Secondary College, the Hoppers Club and many other shopping opportunities.
Conveniently located near the Werribee Mercy and St Vincents Private Hospital, freeway access, train station and a bus stop n Mossfiel Drive.
With a location that is second to none, this rarely seen opportunity deserves your immediate attention.

Description:
!!Nomination Sale Ellarook Street Truganina!!
Bal Real Estate Proudly presents You this great opportunity to build your dream home, on this West Facing 544sqm(approx.) titled block of land in the highly sought after Ellarook estate in Truganina. Ellarook is one of the most exciting new developments in the west. Its size is impressive enough, but wait until you discover what else makes up this landmark estate - Ellarook will feature so much to be proud of.
WELCOME TO A LIFE INSPIRED:
Inspiration comes from many places. But when that place is set in the heart of Melbourne's thriving west, surrounded by the best life has to offer and just 25 minutes from the city, it becomes an inspired opportunity for you and your family. Welcome to Ellarook, where a real community will enjoy an inspired life.
Ellarook residents can look forward to their own train station, just across the road when the future Truganina train station opens, bringing added convenience to the growing area.
Ellarook create a balanced, healthy & connected way of life that is full of possibilities. At Elements you'll feel instantly welcomed. Explore waterways and parks creating a community for you to build a future for your family. Located in Truganina, you will be spoil for choice with an abundance of community facilities and transport links that give you access to all of life's necessities.
Located in Ellarook Estate, this property is situated in one of the best estates of Truganina. The property is located close to a range of convenient amenities including a future school, shopping center, and purposed Truganina railway station. With future cycling trails, wetlands, picnic areas and playgrounds within walking distance, this property is perfectly positioned.
Within close distance to Tarneit train stations and nearby bus lines is designed to give the entire family easy access to the things that matter, starting with the essentials like Schools, Parks, Transport System and Supermarkets. And if you need to get into the city, Williams Landing or Tarneit train stations and easy access to the Princes Freeway will make it even quick and easy.
21 km to CBD through M1 freeway. This lot is in close proximity to established popular schools such as Truganina P9 school, Westbourne Grammar School, Al-Taqwa College, Williams Landing, Tarneit Train Stations, proposed Truganina Train Station, Parks, Walking Tracks, Local Community Centre, Shops, this wont last long!
It is an address perfectly positioned for convenience and growth. A place where you will take pride in your community and where your neighbors will become your friends.
An opportunity like this is rare to come by and will not last long! To be a part of this exciting experience, living a balanced and active lifestyle at Ellarook Estate, please call Bal on 0413 870 550 or Harpreet Mangat on 0416 412 414 to find out more!

Description:
!!The Dream Opportunity In A Supreme Location!!
Bal Real Estate Proudly presents You this great opportunity to build your dream home, on this beautiful North facing 400M2 titled block of land in the highly sought after Mt Atkinson estate in Truganina.
Belong to Melbourne's new west at Mt. Atkinson, a brand new community in Truganina that will ultimately be home to up to 5,000 families.It's a place to call home, designed to deliver job opportunities and every aspect of quality living,including healthcare, education, connectivity, parks and amenities for an active lifestyle.
Just 25km from the CBD ,With easy freeway access, train stations and local bus stops nearby, Mt Atkinson connects you directly to the heart of Melbourne. This well-sized 400m2 (approx.) block of land in Mt Atkinson Estate is positioned in a prime pocket of Truganina in Melbourne's West.
The Melbourne Business Park at Mt. Atkinson will be a new commercial and employment hub for the region, delivering around 19,000 jobs in a well serviced, connected and attractive environment. The major precinct will give residents the chance to work close to home and provide business owners with the ideal space to grow and prosper, while the future town centre will also open up further employment opportunities.
Retail therapy will take on a new meaning at our future Westfield Town Centre. This exciting new shopping mecca will be a popular destination for everything from daily needs to the latest fashions, as well as dining and entertainment experiences. Healthcare and community services will also be available in this vibrant precinct.
Three quality schools will be delivered at Mt. Atkinson to nurture young minds, providing the perfect place to raise a family in a safe and friendly community. Plans for the community include a government primary school, private primary school and private secondary school, adding to the many educational facilities already in place in the surrounding area.
It is an address perfectly positioned for convenience and growth. A place where you will take pride in your community and where your neighbors will become your friends.
An opportunity like this is rare to come by and will not last long! To be a part of this exciting experience, living a balanced and active lifestyle at Mt Atkinson, please call Harpreet on 0416 412 414 or Bal on 0413 870 550 to find out more!

Description:
Style, Comfort & Loads Of Character!
Beautifully presented with a unique double storey layout full of depth and character, this 4-bedroom family home is primed for living and entertaining.
Enjoying a quiet position opposite a reserve with bus stops on the main road, this sought-after location is surrounded by quality schools and in walking distance of the shops and cafés of CS Square.
Stylish timber floorboards add contemporary flair to the light-filled ground floor, starting with a formal lounge before flowing into generous open plan living and dining zones. The spacious kitchen showcases stone benchtops, stainless steel appliances and a cosy breakfast bar with room for the whole family.
Upstairs youll find 3 sizeable bedrooms plus a study/home office, each serviced by a tidy central bathroom and separate toilet. Privately positioned downstairs, the large main bedroom features a walk-through wardrobe and floor-to-ceiling tiled ensuite with shared access to a guest powder room.
Dual double doors from the living/dining open to a stunning covered alfresco deck and rear patio area, perfect for outdoor entertaining under the pergola with plenty of easy-care grassed space for kids and pets to play. There is a secure double garage and a garden shed for extra storage.
Growing families will adore this feature-packed home in the increasingly popular Caroline Springs area, so call Robert Talevski on 0412 303 128 to find out more about this property.
